<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-18 12:39 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5134 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-XFILES-MOVIE-NYTSF &LR;      06-18 2940
