<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-18 13:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5219 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HANDYMAN-HOTTON-BOS &LR;      06-18 0930
