medical researcher at the National Institutes of Health, is turning
the world of immunology upside down with her radical theory
suggesting that the human immune system is activated not by alien
substances in the body, but by dangerous ones _ the Danger Theory
of immunology. By Claudia Dreifus.  &UR; Moved 6-15. With photo. &LR;
</P>
