   ATWORK-COLUMN (Kansas City, Mo.) _ Meetings bring out the kid in
us. Workplace column by DIANE STAFFORD. Story will move in the
``f'' category.
</P>
<P>
   GUSEWELLE-COLUMN (Undated) _ Getting an urge to leave all the
faulty doorknobs behind. Column by C.W. GUSEWELLE. Story will move
in the ``k'' category.
