   TOP
</P>
<P>
   Lead story:
</P>
<P>
   OIL-SMUGGLE (Washington) _ Large volumes of oil are being
smuggled in violation of the sanctions, and the Clinton
administration is ignoring it. By James Risen. (We plan to move the
story by 9 p.m. ET in ``i'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   Top center story:
</P>
<P>
   3-col. photo reefer to: HOLBROOKE-PROFILE, RICHARDSON-PROFILE;
stories inside.
