<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-18 21:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6235 &Cx1f; tta-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GLOBE-COLUMNIST-NYT &LR;      06-18 1073
